His name is Master, Savior,
Lion of Judah,
Blessed Prince of Peace.

Shepherd, Fortress,
Rock of Salvation,
Lamb of God is He.

Son of David,
King of the Ages,
Eternal Life,
Holy Lord of Glory,
His name is Life.

